			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel, display moving range of unit:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Color code units, scroll message window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select unit, unit menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Menu, pause:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Scroll map:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button + D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom map:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate map right or left:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 or L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change camera angle:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Change units under cursor:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Help menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font><br><br>
