          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Unlock Beowulf -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Read the rumors at Goland, go to Lesalia, then agree to accompany Beowulf to Goland. After a series of plot battles, he joins the party</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Biblos Aquired -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">after clearing all ten levels of the Deep Dungeon</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Cloud -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After returning Reis to human form, go to Goug. Cloud will run off to Zarghidas after a scene. After clearing Igros, go to Zargidas and win the fight</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Dragon Reis -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Accompany Beowulf through Goland Coal City; Reis is rescued during the final battle in the series</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Human Reis -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Read the rumors at Zeltennia, buy a flower in Zarghidas, then return to Goug. This unlocks a battle in Zeltennia, and Reis takes human form afterward</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Unlock Worker 8 -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After rescuing Reis from Goland, return to Goug Machine City. Worker 8 joins the party after a small scene</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite Money -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8005483C E0FF<br>8005483E 05F5</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Level Up -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801904B8 63FF<br>80190678 63FF<br>80190838 63FF<br>
801909F8 63FF<br>80190BB8 63FF</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
